node.text:
As summer approaches and many people are looking at online courses, I want to take the opportunity to remind you all that I have a course on Class 101 in character design! It contains prerecorded lectures and demos and personalized feedback from me on your class projects. So anyone wanting advice on comics or character design from me can look here! 

#comics #webcomics #emmy #emmytherobot #characterdesign
